import React from 'react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Container,
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Box,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardMedia,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  AccountCircle,
  Info,
  ContactSupport,
  CalendarMonth,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Home = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <>
      {/* Main Navigation Bar */}
      <AppBar position="static" sx={{ backgroundColor: '#2196f3' }}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flexGrow: 1, cursor: 'pointer' }} onClick={() => navigate('/')}>
            Spital Management
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              startIcon={<AccountCircle />}
              onClick={() => navigate('/register')}
            >
              Register
            </Button>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              startIcon={<CalendarMonth />}
              onClick={() => navigate('/appointment')}
            >
              Appointment
            </Button>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              startIcon={<Info />}
              onClick={() => navigate('/about')}
            >
              About Us
            </Button>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              startIcon={<ContactSupport />}
              onClick={() => navigate('/contact')}
            >
              Contact Us
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>

      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          bgcolor: '#e3f2fd',
          pt: 8,
          pb: 6,
          backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #bbdefb 100%)',
        }}
      >
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Typography
            component="h1"
            variant="h2"
            color="primary"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', textAlign: 'center' }}
          >
            Welcome to Spital Management
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="h5"
            color="text.secondary"
            paragraph
            sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 4 }}
          >
            Your trusted healthcare management system
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Main Content */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 8 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/featured/?hospital"
                alt="Hospital"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                  Register Now
                </Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Join our healthcare system to access medical services.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  color="primary"
                  sx={{ mt: 2 }}
                  onClick={() => navigate('/register')}
                >
                  Register
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/featured/?healthcare"
                alt="Healthcare"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                  About Our Services
                </Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Learn more about our healthcare services and facilities.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  color="primary"
                  sx={{ mt: 2 }}
                  onClick={() => navigate('/about')}
                >
                  Learn More
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/featured/?medical"
                alt="Medical"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                  Contact Support
                </Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Get in touch with our healthcare professionals.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  color="primary"
                  sx={{ mt: 2 }}
                  onClick={() => navigate('/contact')}
                >
                  Contact Us
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
};

export default Home;
